{"type": "article", "id": 15230, "title": "幻想桌灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-22T06:38:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115213OXW5RykC4JUD3EoB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏灯身上有一个充满童趣的设计，三角形的支架下不仅能插木棍，还能插上勺、锅刷之类的厨房物品，让平时常见或者闲置不用的东西多了一份功能。灯泡的角度能随着物品的改变相应调整高度，但保持微微上扬的姿态，有一种探寻的意味，且始终生动活泼。<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/little-fantasia-table-lamp/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261425020aWZMDVPOcqtwEiL.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"940\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142503ftr8VJzZoHMsY3D5.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"1066\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.13404255\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142504mY2CE8fNg1u6aqVb.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"1331\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.41595745\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}